flowchart TB
    subgraph Odoo["ODOO POS SYSTEM"]
        A[POS Transaction] --> B{Configuration Check}
        B -->|Real-Time| C[Immediate Sync]
        B -->|Scheduled| D[Queue for EOD]
        B -->|Manual| E[Wait for User Action]

        C --> F[API Client]
        D --> G[Cron Job 00:00]
        E --> H[Manual Sync Wizard]

        G --> I[Consolidation Service]
        H --> I

        I --> J[Group by Shop+Date]
        J --> K[Aggregate Line Items]
        K --> F

        F --> L[HTTP POST]
    end

    subgraph NetSuite["NETSUITE ERP"]
        M --> N{Validate Payload}
        N -->|Invalid| O[Return Error]
        N -->|Valid| P[Check Duplicates]

        P --> Q[Create Invoice]
        Q --> R[Create Payments]
        R --> S[Return Success]
    end

    O -.-> T[Log Error Retry Logic]
    S -.-> U[Update Sync Status]

    T --> F
    U --> V[Mark Orders as Synced]

    style A fill:#e1f5ff
    style M fill:#fff4e1
    style F fill:#d4edda
    style I fill:#d4edda
